Praia das Conchas is a nice Portuguese owned pousada with a small pool . Near the center and about 100m from the beach. Rooms were about R$80 for a couple with small breakfast in March 2011. Website: http://conchas.no.comunidades.net/index.php. Phone: (82) 3272-1685.
Praia do Gunga is a beautiful beach across the bay, about 20 minutes away by car. There is also a lookout point called Mirante do Gunga which offers a nice view of the beach.
